<F P=102>   LD2806163694 Warsaw PAP in English 1243 GMT 28 Jun 94 -- FOR 
OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> LD2806163694 </F>
<F P=104>  Warsaw PAP </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Warsaw, June 28 -- Prime Minister Waldemar Pawlak on 
Tuesday recalled Wlodzimierz Dabkowski from the post of 
undersecretary of state at the ministry of agriculture and food 
economy, the government press office reported. On the motion of 
the agriculture minister, the prime minister appointed Katarzyna 
Duczkowska-Malysz undersecretary of state at the ministry on 
Tuesday. 

</TEXT>

