<H3> <TI>   Ministers To Report to Sansaricq's Office </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Ministers To Report to Sansaricq's Office </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   FL3105202794 Port-au-Prince Radio Metropole in French 1045 
