<F P=100> Bolivia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Court Justices' Impeachment Suspended by Congressional Recess </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Court Justices' Impeachment Suspended by Congressional Recess </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PY0106032694 La Paz Television Nacional Network in Spanish 
0100 GMT 1 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> PY0106032694 </F>
<F P=104>  La Paz Television Nacional Network </F>
<F P=105>  Spanish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpt] The Senate has suspended the impeachment of 
[Supreme Court Justices] Edgar Oblitas and Ernesto Pope. 
  Senate President Juan Carlos Duran has stated that the 
impeachment was suspended in compliance with a decision by the 
Congress stating that the two houses cannot work separately. A 
few days ago the Chamber of Deputies declared a recess until 6 
June, and the Senate had to follow suit and thus suspend the 
impeachment process. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

